# RELEASE — squid-tumbleweed-config

Version:  v3.3
Date:     2026-04-30
Platform: openSUSE Tumbleweed
Squid:    7.4

---

## What's in this release

### v3.3 — HaGeZi PRO++ ad list + Google admin UI whitelist
- ACL `yoyo_ads` renamed to `ads_block` — reflects the actual source list now in use
- Ad list source: pgl.yoyo.org (~3,500 domains) → HaGeZi PRO++ (~233,600 domains)
- New ACL `google_admin_ui` for Search Console, GA admin, Tag Manager admin
- `http_access allow google_admin_ui` placed before `deny CONNECT ads_block`
  — admin UIs work even though their domains may appear in the ad-block list
- Tracker beacons (www.google-analytics.com, googletagmanager.com, doubleclick.net …)
  remain blocked at DNS level via [unbound-tumbleweed-config](https://github.com/crisis1er/unbound-tumbleweed-config)

---

### v3.2 — CVE-2025-54574 mitigation + HTTP TRACE block
- `acl URN proto URN` + `http_access deny URN` — mitigates CVE-2025-54574 (URN heap buffer overflow RCE)
- `acl HTTP_TRACE method TRACE` + `http_access deny HTTP_TRACE` — blocks XST attacks
- Removed redundant `cachemgr_passwd` directive (manager already restricted via ACL)
- Removed `acl gopher_proto proto GOPHER` — protocol removed from Squid 7.4
- Squid version reference updated: 6.x → 7.4

---

### v3.1 — Tightened squid.conf permissions
- Restricted `squid.conf` to `640 root:root` — Lynis SQD-3613 hardening

---

### v3.0 — Multi-AI / streaming / dev support
- New ACLs: `ai_zml` (.z.ai), `ai_kimi` (.kimi.ai .moonshot.cn .moonshot.ai)
- New ACLs: `vpn_nordvpn`, `dev_github`
- Streaming: extended `streaming_twitch` with full CDN
- WebSocket (`CONNECT`) support for ZML and Kimi
- `refresh_pattern` for `.iso` and `.img` (cache up to 1 year)
- Delay pools: ISO/image downloads throttled to 10 MB/s (burst 20 MB)
- `cache deny` for ai_zml and ai_kimi — real-time responses
- `pipeline_prefetch 0` — prevents head-of-line blocking on multi-worker setup

---

## Current configuration summary

| Parameter            | Value                                |
|----------------------|--------------------------------------|
| Workers              | 4                                    |
| Listen port          | 10000                                |
| Disk cache           | 1 GB (diskd)                         |
| Memory cache         | 512 MB per worker                    |
| DNS                  | Unbound 127.0.0.1 / ::1              |
| TLS policy           | PROFILE=SYSTEM — NO_SSLv3/TLSv1/1.1  |
| Ad blocking          | HaGeZi PRO++ (~233,600 domains)      |
| Header anonymization | forwarded_for delete, via off        |
